  "description": "Hard sync at fifth interval (7 semitones), Twitch curiosity targeting filter cutoff — brief irregular stabs at the filter. Short attack, medium sustain. The visual signature of the clownfish as audio: orange-white-orange, never predictably spaced. Each MIDI note a flash in a different direction.",
